name: Deborah Goldberg

name: Deborah Goldberg

name: Deborah Goldberg

name: Deborah Goldberg
tweet: Take the first step! Save today for your child's tomorrow! Every child who is a Massachusetts resident is eligible to receive a $50 deposit into a  https://t.co/O9FgPdZBCm 529 College Investing Plan within one year of their birth or adoption.   https://t.co/qnk3FnU8Zc

name: Deborah Goldberg
tweet: Treasurer Goldberg and Deputy Treasurer Alayna Van Tassel joined @NEFE_ORG podcast to discuss #financialeducation, examples of initiatives @EmpowermentMA has started and the benefits of replicating them in other states.  Click ⬇️to watch!   https://t.co/5uI5H4MNi8

name: Deborah Goldberg
tweet: #EqualPay for equal work continues to be out of reach for people across Massachusetts because of their gender, race, sexual orientation, and/or disability. We held this event to focus on raising awareness and working towards narrowing the #wagegap.  Watch ⬇️!

name: Deborah Goldberg
tweet: At @masstreasury we are heartbroken to hear of the passing of Madeleine Albright. Dr. Albright dedicated her life to #HumanRights and equality. She exemplified strength and the footprint she has left will never be forgotten. Her legacy will live on for generations to come.

name: Deborah Goldberg
tweet: Have you checked out our EqualPayMA’s “Employer Tool Kit”? It's a guide designed to help identify, understand, and promote #equalpay in the workplace. This Tool Kit includes easy and innovative solutions to help employers close the #genderwagegap.   https://t.co/Fj3CmhsQpR
